latestVersion.termsOfAccess:
Project files like raw data, coding guidelines and questionnaires can now be directly downloaded from this site.
Please see also SSD's Farm Household Survey Database (http://ricestat.irri.org/fhsd/).
latestVersion.dataAccessPlace: All files for this project/study, except for the Project Description, need to be directly downloaded from SSD's Farm Household Survey Database's online link: http://ricestat.irri.org/fhsd/

fields.value: The Effects of Pumping on Water Use and Profitability in dry season rice:  A case study in Upper Pampanga River Irrigation System (UPRIIS), Philippines

authorName.value: Piedad, Moya and Valencia, Ma. Shiela

dsDescriptionValue.value: To compare economic performance of rice production and water management practices of farmers in different water delivery systems in UPRIIS.

keywordValue.value: Input-output of crop production (yield, material inputs, labor, prices, disposal of production) and water management practices (frequency and duration of irrigation, fuel use, cumulative depth of water)

fields.value: Subject: Number of Repondents  Type: Sample Size  Notes: 60;
